Locate Swashbuckler - information/theme skill
------------------------------------------------------------
Swashbucklers are a close brotherhood, and tend to know each
other very well. Drawing on this knowledge, it is possible
for one swashbuckler to imagine himself at the side of
another, and actually catch a glimpse that other's immediate
surroundings.

Should you not desire to be found, use 'slocate off' to
prevent others from locating you. 'Slocate on' will allow
them to do so once more.

GL:  6
SP: 10
command:  slocate on/off/<who>
duration: instant
